1. *Žrtve* su stradale u ratu. (The victims suffered in the war.)

2. Oni su donirali za *žrtve* poplave. (They donated for the victims of the flood.)

3. Oni su postali bolesne *žrtve* civilizacije. (They became sick victims of civilization.)

4. Oni su se žrtvovali za svoju zemlju. (They sacrificed themselves for their country.)

5. Oni su bili žrtve svojih emocija. (They were victims of their emotions.)